javascript framework, build web application :spa - single page applications, compact compared to jquery, js
open source
madewithangular.com: shows sites built with angularjs
1) dependency injection
2) 2 way data binding: keeps model and view sync at all time
3) easy to test: unit (jasmine framework)+ integration
4) MVC apps, directives, filters, modules, routes..

---------------------------
Steps to build angularjs app:
1) From angularjs.org download angular.js script file, add it to html page.
ng-app is a directive , starting point for angular application, can be added to html, body , div tags
ng-model: to set field in the model from view page.